Package com.simsilica.mathd

Class Vec3d

java.lang.Object
com.simsilica.mathd.Vec3d
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class Vec3d extends Object implements Cloneable
A vector composed of 3 double-precision components, used to represent locations, offsets, and directions in 3-dimensional space.
